categories          devel
platforms           any
supported_archs     noarch
license             MIT
maintainers         nomaintainer

description         Zero-runtime dependency manager for package managers
long_description    Corepack is a zero-runtime dependency manager for \
                    package managers, meant to improve the experience of \
                    using yarn, pnpm, and npm. It acts as a bridge between \
                    your projects and the package managers you intend to \
                    use in them, allowing you to use the package manager \
                    configured in a project's packageManager field from \
                    anywhere in the project's directory tree.

